data.description: Absolutely beautiful and completely renovated Golf Club Drive Townhome. Move in ready with the finest of high end finishes. Golf Club home ownership includes an exclusive lifestyle of endless amenities that begin as you drive through the front gate (24 hour security guard) Two pools (1 lagoon style, 1 smaller lap pool) Renovated fitness center; Two cars permitted on-street-parking. The seller has done an exquisite job remodeling with a keen eye for detail. including; A newly renovated kitchen and half bath addition; A laundry closet  also an addition; Interior painting (Sherwin Williams Alabaster) Exterior house painted including fences and porches; Rebuilt front, rear porches, steps and front fence; Lanai screen and trim replaced. Deeded rear extended yard is fully fenced (5ft+ tall fencing) Upscale turf in yard and under the house; Newly installed Centurion stone pavers extending from the front walkway to the rear outdoor patio; Phillips Hue Hardscape Lightening with app control. Upgraded D electrical panel, Decora outlets and switches installed throughout entire home, all remote operated ceiling fans and flush mount lighting downstairs have dimmers. New (2023) kitchen appliance suite with Kitchenaid convection range and quiet wash dishwasher. Subzero fridge/freezer combo unit remains. Kraftmaid solid maple cabinetry with slide out shelving. Downstairs has engineered hardwood flooring throughout. Upstairs features two primary bedrooms both with glorious vaulted ceiling, NEW remote dimmable ceiling fans. 2nd Primary has porch access with new French Doors. Larger primary bedroom overlooks the preserve along the golf course where you will enjoy endless sunrises and sunsets. The entire upper level has newly installed LVP flooring with 20 year commercial grade rating. Community pool is heated. AT&T, high-speed Internet included in the HOA. DIRECTV streaming cable and Internet equipment also included. Call to schedule a private showing.
